::DarkMouse::
She couldn't believe it. He was honored to have HER as a partner. She was 
about to start jumping up and down. And he said she was beautiful?
She never thought that she was beautiful. Good looking maybe, but not that 
good looking.  She was blushing so hard her face looked like a red emergency 
light.
"uh, why thank you commander for the compliment. I.. uh.. I like you too.  I 
like you alot actually. Um, I don't know what to say."
She felt her face turn an even deeper red. She was wondering if her spark 
would explode.  Did she love him? is this what it feel like?
